caption: b'Happy Thanksgiving from the Nexon family to your family! :turkey::maple_leaf: We are so thankful for all your support and wish you and yours a safe holiday filled with joy and gratitude :smiling_face_with_3_hearts:'
b'Happy #NationalPrincessDay to some of our faves from @KRRushPlus and @V4Global! :princess::crown::two_hearts:#PrincessDay'

b"Just two more days until #MapleStoryFest2020 :partying_face: The date and time is easy to remember: 11/11 at 11AM PT! :keycap_1::keycap_1::alarm_clock: It'll be a ton of fun with Maplers from all over the world :globe_showing_Americas: AND lots of gifts and rewards :wrapped_gift: will be given out so see you all then at http://twitch.tv/maplestory! :red_heart_selector:"

b"Happy Halloween from Nexon to you! :jack-o-lantern::ghost::skull: We wish you a festive holiday weekend - remember to stay safe no matter what your plans are (we'll be taking advantage of the Halloween events in some of our games :winking_face:) ! :clown_face::ogre::goblin::smiling_face_with_horns::cowboy_hat_face::partying_face: @nxdarknessrises @playmaplem @mabiofficial @kartriderdrift @maplestory"

b"All the awesome CMs in our Nexon America family will be hosting a fun-filled stream on twitch.tv/maplestory that will cover all our games, starting today at 11AM PT! :star-struck: There will be giveaways for all games so don't miss out on this big Halloween party! :partying_face:"

b"Happy #NationalCat Day to all the feline lovers out there! To celebrate, we wanted to share a couple of in-game cats (@V4Global, @MabiOfficial  @playmaplem) as well as some real-life cats from our Nexon family! :grinning_cat_face::smiling_cat_face_with_heart-eyes::kissing_cat_face:If you slide through, there's a video of a Nexie's cat cleaning his desk for him every morning :cat_face_with_tears_of_joy: Tag us in your pics of your feline friends (in-game or real life)! :cat_face:"

b"What's everyone's #Halloween2020 plans? :eyes: We're going to stay in Maple World :maple_leaf:, where Halloween is already in full swing:skull::ghost::jack-o-lantern::smiling_face_with_horns:Don't wait until the end of the month - get your spooky on and play @maplestory and @playmaplem now! :raising_hands:"

b'For a long time, Nexon has rewarded an employee every month who\'s had impactful contributions with company-wide recognition, a gift card, and a plaque with their name on it. :glowing_star: Now, we want to share these spotlighted Nexies and their insights with everyone in a monthly series! :sparkles:\n\nStarting with Nicole Kim! :star-struck: She is a self-identified "gaming nerd" :video_game: who loves playing RPGs and catching up on shows in her spare time. She\'s worked for other mobile gaming companies & Nexon is lucky to have her as part of our team since the beginning of this year. :smiling_face_with_smiling_eyes: :sparkling_heart:'

b'Maplers, we want to showcase you at #MapleStoryFest2020! :sparkles: \nBe a part AND win awesome prizes by joining our community video, our cosplay contest, and/or our fanart contest! :maple_leaf::smiling_face_with_smiling_eyes::sparkling_heart: \nVisit maplestoryfest.com, or swipe up on our story for the link to submit your videos and talents!'

b"Hey Riders! Have you tried the SONATA N Line Kart in @kartriderrushplus? We teamed up with @hyundaiusa to bring it to you:smiling_face_with_sunglasses: :chequered_flag: It's quick off the starting line with precision handling that can cut through the competition!:racing_car_selector: :dashing_away: :dashing_away: Let us know what you think!"

b"Maplers, have you heard the exciting news? :partying_face::party_popper: MapleStory Fest is coming to your homes this year, and it's FREE! Go to maplestoryfest.com for more details and to register for our raffle!! :wrapped_gift::raising_hands: @maplestory @playmaplem"
b'Happy first day of October! :skull: :ghost:\n:woman_dancing::man_dancing::musical_note: ~Spooky, scary officer skeletons~:musical_note::woman_dancing::man_dancing: #MapleStory @MapleStory'

b'Yesterday, we held an in-office free flu shot clinic for Nexies and their families! :stethoscope::syringe::adhesive_bandage:Health and safety is always our priority, so as we continue to WFH, we offered this optional benefit while following all safety guidelines. :man_health_worker_selector::adult:\xe2\x80\x8d:medical_symbol_selector::woman_health_worker_selector:Thank you to all healthcare workers who keep us healthy! :red_heart_selector:'

b'We\'re loving your "I grew up here" challenge answers featuring our games!\xc2\xa0:smiling_face_with_3_hearts:\xc2\xa0This is a round-up of some highlights\xc2\xa0:red_heart_selector:\xc2\xa0It\'s been awesome reminiscing with you all, follow us on Twitter or Facebook to join the discussion there:\xc2\xa0twitter.com/Nexon_America & facebook.com/nexonamerica/ We will also be sharing the links in our story!'
b'Happy #FirstDayOfFall from our team to yours! :smiling_face_with_smiling_eyes:  Do you have a favorite fall activity? :fallen_leaf: :maple_leaf: :jack-o-lantern: #AutumnEquinox'

b'To keep safe during these unprecedented times, Nexies are continuing to #workfromhome away from our beautiful campus until at least the end of 2020\xc2\xa0:red_heart_selector:\xc2\xa0And we are continuing to hire - Join the fun and apply today :smiling_face_with_smiling_eyes::glowing_star:\xc2\xa0Go to the link in our bio now!'

b':loudspeaker:Calling all Milletians :double_exclamation_mark_selector: The Nexon Merch Store is now stocked with cute @mabiofficial character acrylic figures :smiling_face_with_heart-eyes::raising_hands: Happy shopping on http://merch.nexon.net :shopping_bags_selector::glowing_star::smiling_face_selector:'

b"Repost from @MapleStory for the ultimate throwback & nostalgia :hugging_face: ... It's Saturday morning, 2007. You're free! Time for cartoons. TV on, you get this :face_with_tears_of_joy: :pig_face: :top_hat: (#sorrynotsorry) #tbt :grinning_squinting_face:"

b":party_popper: @V4Global has reached 1M downloads since its launch last month!:smiling_face_with_heart-eyes::confetti_ball: Our V4 team's so thankful that so many of you love to #PlayV4, and they want to show their appreciation with a special one-time event:smiling_face_with_sunglasses: It's ending tomorrow - don't miss out! Details :backhand_index_pointing_right:https://bit.ly/2YivMgy"

:folded_hands: Thanks for being part of our journey and all your support.
